snippet.title: Official UK PlayStation Magazine - Net Yaroze - Arena
snippet.description:
This is a video of the Net Yaroze game Arena, created by Tom Madens.

It was featured on Official UK PlayStation Magazine's demo disc 108.

In the video I attempt the first level of the game.
